# MCP environment variables
# Copy this file to mcps/.env and fill in your values.
# mcps/.env is gitignored — never commit real secrets.
#
# Variables listed here are passed to MCP servers at install time:
#   - Claude Code: stored permanently in the MCP server config
#   - opencode:    written to ~/.config/opencode/config.json under the MCP's env field
#
# Add a key here when a registry.json entry uses it in "required_env" or "env".

# Example — uncomment and fill in if you add an MCP that needs it:
# SOME_API_KEY=your_key_here
